<p><a href="http://journals.aps.org/prl/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevLett.110.117001">5. Experimental Evidence for s-Wave Pairing Symmetry in Superconducting CuxBi2Se3 Single Crystals Using a Scanning Tunneling Microscope(PRL2013)</a></p>

