<p><a href="http://journals.aps.org/prb/abstract/10.1103/PhysRevB.86.094507">8. Rotational isotropy breaking as proof for spin-polarized Cooper pairs in the topological superconductor CuxBi2Se3(PRB2012)</a></p>

